high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the fridge
pick up a cup from the fridge
move to the microwave behind you
heat the cup in the microwave
move to the coffee maker behind you
put the cup on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Push over the two knives in the center of the counter flat. Then turn to the right to go around the island, and find the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and take out a mug.
Carry the mug and turn to the right. Locate the microwave on the left side counter.
Place the mug inside the microwave and turn it on. Open the microwave and then take out the mug and shut the door.
Take the mug and turn to the left to go around the island. Find the coffee machine on the counter on the other side of the room.
Place the mug under the coffee machine.
Turn right, go forward, turn left, go a bit forward, turn right and go to the fridge
Open the fridge, pick up the mug in the fridge, close the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward a bit, turn right, go forward, turn left at the microwave
Open the microwave, put the mug in it, close the microwave, start the microwave, wait, open the microwave, pick up the mug, close the microwave
Turn left, go around the table in the middle, turn right at the end of the counter
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Warm a cup to make coffee
